SUMMARY TABLE
================================================================

 API                  | Requires Key | Works Offline | Used For
----------------------+--------------+---------------+------------------
 Firebase Firestore   | Yes          | Yes (queued)  | Database / sync
 Nominatim            | No           | No            | Address lookup
 BigDataCloud         | No           | No            | Address fallback
 PhilSMS              | Yes          | No*           | SMS alerts
 Open-Meteo           | No           | No            | Weather data
 Overpass API         | No           | No            | Evacuation map
 Leaflet              | No           | Yes (cached)  | Map rendering
 OSM Tile Server      | No           | Yes (cached)  | Map images
 Tailwind CSS CDN     | No           | Yes (cached)  | UI styling
 Google Fonts         | No           | Yes (cached)  | Typography

 * PhilSMS falls back to native SMS app when offline.

